		  <t>The fields are defined as follows:

		  <list style="hanging">
            <t hangText="Geneve Protocol Type">TBD value for IOAM.</t>

            <t hangText="Type:">8-bit unsigned integer defining IOAM header
            type. Four values are defined here: IOAM_Trace_Preallocated,
            IOAM_Trace_Incremental, IOAM_POT, and IOAM_E2E.</t>

            <t hangText="IOAM HDR len:">8-bit unsigned integer. Length of the
            IOAM HDR in 4-octet units.</t>

            <t hangText="Next Protocol:">16-bit unsigned integer that
            determines the type of the protocol data unit appearing after
            the IOAM trace option header. This follows the EtherType
            <xref target="ETYPES"/> convention.</t>

          </list></t>

		  <t>The fields of the trace option header 
		  <xref target="I-D.ietf-ippm-ioam-data"/> are as follows: 
		  <list style="hanging">
			
